Setting:
He's sitting in the car listening to the Basketball game. 
He is waiting for her to return. 
He is playing on github, exploring the features.
He receives a text message from his friend asking about late tennis.
It is 5:30pm.

Action:
He texts back 6:15ish? His friend says okay.

Result:
He feels some time pressure. 
He thinks he needs to eat, perhaps drink water.
He anxiously looks towards the beach awaiting her return.
He wonders why he committed or offered such an early time.
